Package com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.position

Class PositionEstimator<P extends com.irurueta.geometry.Point>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.position.PositionEstimator<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - a Point type.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinearPositionEstimator, NonLinearPositionEstimator
    public abstract class PositionEstimator<P extends com.irurueta.geometry.Point>
extends Object
    Base class for position estimators using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations. These kind of estimators can be used to determine the position of a given device by getting readings at an unknown location of different radio sources whose locations are known.
